  <prompt>Run the `jps-scope-refresh` skill. Verify the PlaybookBuilder scope catalog reflects the new `BRIEF-NARRATE` playbook + any reconciled playbook configs from tasks 011 + 015. Capture the refresh log in `notes/deployments/016-scope-refresh.md`.</prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Follow ADRs strictly. JPS scope-catalog operator.</role>

  <goal>The PlaybookBuilder scope catalog (the JSON the UI reads to render playbook + action lists) reflects the post-PR-2 deployed state of spaarkedev1. Refresh log captured.</goal>

